        <section class="container-fluid">

            <h2 class="section-heading">Impact of Drug Abuse</h2>

            <p class="blurb">

                Drug abuse among teens has significantly increased, with overdose deaths doubling from 2019 to
                2020 and over two-thirds of high school seniors trying alcohol.

                <br><br>

                This behavior can lead to problems at
                school, mental health issues, motor-vehicle accidents, and place stress on families.

            </p>

            <div class="row row-l">

