                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">

                    <h2 class="header">Physical Health</h2>
                    <p class="impact-text">
                        Drug abuse can cause physical effects such as organ damage, physical dependence, and
                        increased risk of health problems. It can also lead to impaired judgment and coordination, and
                        increased risk of mental health disorders.
                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="row row-r">

