                    <h2 class="header">Mental Health</h2>
                    <p class="impact-text">
                        Drug abuse can cause mental and emotional problems such as depression, anxiety, psychosis,
                        and cognitive impairment, and can worsen existing mental health issues. It can also cause
                        psychosis and impair cognitive function.
                    </p>

                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6 shown">
